		    curconfig[DiskCache].val.i ? WEBKIT_CACHE_MODEL_WEB_BROWSER :
		    WEBKIT_CACHE_MODEL_DOCUMENT_VIEWER);

		/* Currently only works with text file to be compatible with curl */
